"controversial" to the far left woke brigade.
There is no reason these migrants cannot stay in France, or any of the other half dozen European countries they have already passed through. They don't need to pass the English channel to get into the UK when they're perfectly safe in France and can live there. So why should the UK be obligated to accept them when they're already safe where they are? UK has no obligation at all, so the migrants can either stay in France or go to Rwanda, either choice leaves them in a positive safe position and at the expense to the British taxpayer.
